{"tid":523942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙漠落雪】撒哈拉沙漠罕見落雪 40厘米積雪蓋黃沙","createTime":"2018-01-09T05:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T08:13:35.000Z","uid":144549,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ce916d30b053b37a62ba24574ee0ad9bb0a08c03","tid":523942,"uid":144549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180109/large/1515458779_9e41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180109%2Flarge%2F1515458779_9e41.jpg&h=8a69a216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n非洲撒哈拉沙漠今年再出現罕見披雪奇景，是40年來的第三次。<br />\n<br />\n阿爾及利亞西北部小鎮艾因塞弗拉（Ain Sefra）周日凌晨落雪，鎮內積雪1至2吋，郊區沙丘也蓋上白雪。當地人錄得多達40厘米（16吋）的降雪量。<br />\n<br />\n攝影師Karim Bouchetata表示，那天一覺醒來再見到白雪皚皚，感到十分詫異。雪景維持到下午5點融雪為止。<br />\n<br />\n氣象局解釋，歐洲周末高氣壓，令冷空氣向南擴展至北非。<br />\n<br />\n艾因塞弗拉非常接近摩洛哥邊境，位於海拔1,000米以上，四周被阿特拉斯山脈（Atlas Mountains）包圍，雖處高海拔，但1月份平均氣溫介乎6℃至12℃，鮮有下雪。<br />\n<br />\n今次是艾因塞弗拉40年來第三次披雪。前年12月當地突然罕見下雪，一個月後下了另一場雪。之前，艾因塞弗拉沙漠出現飄雪奇景，要數到1979年2月。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180109/57683916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57683916&d=xX77hroXdMzR4jOVmCMNZY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7ef9ba7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57683916&h=65ccbe9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180109/57683916</a>"},{"pid":"c491d8c72cfbbf01be2e8054848df039eec3c894","tid":523942,"uid":136640,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"反暖化撚全面報到"},{"pid":"72a560dcacd312818cdef8a875c5d573b3a5ea75","tid":523942,"uid":109983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反暖化撚全面報到</blockquote><br />\n撚狗時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32f9894f204d9d6f3ab5a33c89e120d772a0511","tid":523942,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"好出奇呀？"},{"pid":"c9d9a3257745563c4cc88a86e844c5f406242cd6","tid":523942,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"等睇極端天氣撚入黎"},{"pid":"2048b52991a1223dba569cca52339a61dc788abb","tid":523942,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"唔驚無水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd1204716a5c69c72ab9e7e1afc2ef375ad0152","tid":523942,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"北非冬天一向凍"},{"pid":"5e0f18d6727af8f2bd4430ec74722d37d2cbe919","tid":523942,"uid":42374,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"一定有成班中學地理知識都無嘅人衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d9249766b8c92e9fe68d53bbabeee020af4cd4","tid":523942,"uid":50506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"好似灑左堆白沙糖係到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61055731ce8150296a0137c8b25a2ca755aef347","tid":523942,"uid":109983,"like":4,"dislike":49,"score":-45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定有成班中學地理知識都無嘅人衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9先讀地理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbb2d9f2ed7b70c290663e4284c1c54c6a9d87d","tid":523942,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:58:00.